<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١١٥)</span> بابُ كُنْيَةِ الْمُشْرِكِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ مِسْوَرٌ:</span> سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«إِلَّا أَنْ يُرِيدَ ابْنُ أَبِي طَالِبٍ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>